episodes.author: Artie Lange / Radio Misfits
episodes.summary:
The great Brian Jones, one of our DirecTV favorites, joins Artie, Ryan, Geno, and Kevin Dombrowski. The guys wonder what it would sound like at the world’s dumbest clan meeting. They also discuss what Brian’s wife did for a living. A discussion ensues as to what the guys think makes a good talk show host. Artie does a special tribute to David Bowie that you don’t want to miss (and he doesn’t want any relative to profit off of it). Artie also brings up how fascinated he is by the toe nail fungus commercial.
